http://localhost:8000/currency-exchange/from/USD/to/INR

http://localhost:8100/currency-conversion/from/USD/to/INR/quantity/10

Currently, instance of CurrencyExchangeServiceApplication will run on port 8000.
To launch another instance of CurrencyExchangeServiceApplication on different port - 8001 -
    1. go to Edit Configurations (drop down just beside the build hammer icon in intellij)
    2. click plus button to add new Spring Boot config.
    3. Rename this config to CurrencyExchangeServiceApplication8001
    4. Under Configuration tab, copy Main class name from CurrencyExchangeServiceApplication
    5. Under Environments -> VM Options -> add this ->  -Dserver.port=8001
    6. Run


Database H2 -
http://localhost:8000/h2-console


http://localhost:8000/currency-exchange/from/AUD/to/INR

Run below maven goal to create docker image from this service -
mvn spring-boot:build:image -DskipTests

Run docker container using above image -
docker run -p 8000:8000 ravibhai/mmv2-currency-exchange-service:0.0.1-SNAPSHOT

